Template: jitsi-videobridge/jvb-hostname
Type: string
Default: localhost
_Description: Hostname:
 The jisti-videobridge package needs the DNS hostname of your instance.

Template: jitsi-videobridge/advanced
Type: boolean
Default: false
_Description: Proceed with advanced install?
 The default installation should give you a working Jitsi Videobridge 
 instance right away, while the advanced one may help you troubleshoot or
 select installation parameters instead of the defaults and keep the 
 install minimal..
